  <brief_title>Willingness to Pay for Patient-centred Care</brief_title>
  <official_title>Identifying Patients' and Healht Insurers' Preferences Regarding Patient-centred Care by Determining Their Willingness-to-pay for Patient-centred Care</official_title>
  <sponsors>
